{"tid":2277791,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葡萄牙今日起進入緊急狀態　多個城市實施宵禁","createTime":"2020-11-08T17:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T18:26:25.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cbce008eadfcf590624de0b2b0c1b0f5ff9381df","tid":2277791,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T17:26:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558974-20201109.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558974-20201109.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq76ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=0df8d871\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558974-20201109.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7928bed0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558974-20201109.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙的新型肺炎疫情惡化，全國星期一起進入為期15日的緊急狀態，總理科斯塔又宣布，同日起在包括首都里斯本及波圖在內的121個城市或地區，實施宵禁。<br />\n<br />\n宵禁令在每日「晚11朝6」生效，民眾未來兩個星期六及星期日，不可以在下午1時至翌日早上5時離開住所。<br />\n<br />\n當局會在商場、服務機構、地鐵站等公共場所入口強制民眾量體溫，並加派人手進行篩查及跟蹤工作。"},{"pid":"a810b93d47a7fb1ee8b411e1d9eac38fdb7bd88e","tid":2277791,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T17:28:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db9b94cf3e679a71b45ac59752a6ca9bc0411e58","tid":2277791,"uid":124134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T18:26:25.000Z","msg":"其實而家好多國家應該都谷住道氣<br />\n<br />\n想屌鳩中共好耐"}]}